index, fell by 0.75 rupees, or 3.49 percent, to 22.25 rupees with
a volume of 60.130 million shares.
</P>
<P>
The total volume traded stood at 270.452 million shares against
Wednesday's 144.575 million shares.
</P>
<P>
Out of the 154 active issues, losers beat gainers 86 to 29
while 39 remained unchanged. 
