<HEADLINE> Article Refutes "Two States" Statement (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
However, Lee's statement has cast a heavy shadow over relations
across the Taiwan Straits. Stock markets in Taiwan have plunged
and polls show a sharp decline in Lee's popular support in Taiwan.
