<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Close 2.48 Percent Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks were down 336.
68 points, or 2.48 percent, to close at 13,254.34 Thursday.
</P>
