The Hang Seng Index lost 32.91 points, or 0.24 percent, to open
at 13,558.11 points Thursday morning and finished the morning
session at 13,438.82 points.
</P>
<P>
The market turnover totaled 5.6 billion HK dollars (717 million
U.S. dollars), 489 million HK dollars (or 62 million U.S. dollars)
higher than Wednesday's turnover of 5.111 billion HK dollars (655
million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
