<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, August 5 (Xinhua) -- Bangladesh is committed to
maintaining good relations with neighboring countries based on
equality, mutual respect and economic uplift, Foreign Minister
Abdus Samad Azad said here on Thursday.
</P>
