invoices in the house. Police examined a ledger of Li's that
showed that he received 116,649 yuan (some 14,000 US dollars) on
May 4th, 1994.
</P>
<P>
Li Hongzhi also planned to build a "Falun Research Center" in
Huailai County in north China's Hebei Province on 60 hectares of
land.  
